---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import GetQuoete from "../../../components/buttons/GetQuote.astro";
import Testimonials from "../../../components/Testimonials";
import NumberPhone from "../../../components/NumberPhone.astro";
import CountNumber from "../../../components/CountNumber";
import ButtonScrollTop from "../../../components/buttons/ButtonScrollTop";
import SecondFooter from "../../../components/SecondFooter.astro";
---
<head>
  <script
    type="text/partytown"
    async
    src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=GTM-NT3H9XXW"></script>
  <script type="text/partytown">
    window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
    function gtag() {
      dataLayer.push(arguments);
    }
    gtag("js", new Date());

    gtag("config", "GTM-NT3H9XXW");
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->
  <noscript
    ><iframe
      src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=GTM-NT3H9XXW"
      height="0"
      width="0"
      style="display:none;visibility:hidden"></iframe></noscript
  >
  <!-- End Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->
<style>
  .custom-background {
    background:
      linear-gradient(hsla(250, 75%, 5%, 0.5), rgba(6, 3, 21, 0.5)),
      url("/img/motorcycle-new.jpg") center center no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position-y: 40%;
  }

  .footer--img {
    background-image: url("/public/img/footer.webp");
    background-position-y: 3%;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
  }
</style>

<Layout title="Motorcycle Shipping | Cayad Auto Transport">
  <div
    class="container-fluid flex flex-col items-center justify-center custom-background h-[60vh]"
  >
    <div class="w-[80%]">
      <h1
        class="text-white text-[4rem] xs:text-[1.8rem] sm:text-[1.8rem] font-bold"
        data-aos="fade-down"
      >
        Motorcycle Shipping: Easy and Convenient
      </h1>
      <p class="text-white text-lg font-semibold">
        Cayad ships motorcycles of all types across all 50 states
      </p>
      <GetQuoete />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 flex justify-center mb-8">
    <Testimonials
      title="Read what other motorcycle enthusiasts say about their delivery experience with Cayad"
      client:load
    />
  </div>

  <div class="w-full flex p-4 justify-center">
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full flex xs:flex-col sm:flex-col justify-around"
    >
      <div class="w-1/2 xs:w-full sm:w-full p-2">
        <h1 class="text-[2.5rem] leading-tight font-bold text-[#19171fd2]">
          Why should you choose Cayad Auto Transport for your motorcycle
          shipment?
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-8">
          With years of experience in the industry, we have honed our services
          to ensure safe and efficient motorcycle transportation. No matter
          where you are located in the USA, we are ready to pick up and deliver
          your motorcycle. Our extensive network allows us to reach every corner
          of the country. We understand the value of your motorcycle, and we
          prioritize its safety throughout the shipping process. Our team uses
          secure and reliable methods to keep your bike in perfect condition. We
          believe in providing top-notch customer support. Our dedicated team is
          available to address any questions or concerns you may have. We
          genuinely care about your satisfaction and strive to offer you the
          best experience possible.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <NumberPhone />
        </div>
      </div>
      <CountNumber client:load />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:flex-col sm:flex-col xs:px-4 sm:px-4 flex justify-between"
    >
      <div class="w-[50%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:mb-8 sm:mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold text-[2.5rem]">
          Motorcycle shipping services made easy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-base mt-8">
          Nationwide motorcycle shipping has never been easier with Cayad Auto
          Transport. We offer two types of motorcycle transport services to our
          customers: Door to door (home delivery) and shipping between
          distribution centers. Home delivery (Door to door) transport is the
          most common and preferred customer solution.
          <br />
          <br />

          When shipping a motorcycle Door to door, our assigned carrier will
          arrive at your location and load your motorcycle onto patented metal
          skids and specialized platforms made specifically for transporting
          motorcycles, scooters and ATVs.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-[40%] xs:w-[100%] sm:w-[100%]">
        <img src="/img/moto-ship.webp" class="rounded-xl" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:px-4 sm:px-4">
      <div
        class="grid mt-8 grid-cols-2 xs:grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-1 w-full gap-6"
      >
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-btn-blue duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.3s"
        >
          <h5 class="mb-2 py-4 text-xl text-[#19171fd2] font-bold">
            Motorcycle shipping and seasonal demand
          </h5>
          <p class="py-4" style="text-align: justify;">
            While most companies base their pricing estimates for transport
            services in relation to seasonal market demand, Cayad Auto Transport
            provides you with a set price not directly influenced by typical
            demand fluctuations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-btn-blue duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.5s"
        >
          <div class="team-item p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0">
            <h5 class="mb-2 py-4 text-xl text-[#19171fd2] font-bold">
              Why should I transport my motorcycle with us?
            </h5>
            <p class="py-4" style="text-align: justify;">
              At Cayad Auto Transport, we have built a reputation as the
              industry-leader in vehicle transport. With more than 3 years of
              experience, we are the number one provider for many of the worlds
              largest OEM manufacturers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="w-full flex mb-8 flex-col items-center xs:min-w-[100%] xs:px-0 sm:min-w-[100%] sm:px-0 mx-auto overflow-hidden px-0"
  >
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:min-w-[100%] xs:px-4 sm:min-w-[100%] sm:px-4 py-10 px-0"
    >
      <h1 class="text-4xl text-[#19171fd2] font-medium mb-10">
        Why should you choose Cayad Auto Transport for enclosed auto transport?
      </h1>
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-1 xs:grid-cols-1 gap-10"
      >
        <div class="wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <img src="/img/countries.webp" class="w-24 h-20 mb-2" />
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold">13K+ auto carriers</h5>
              <p class="xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0">
                Cayad Auto Transport has a huge network of haulers who are
                personally vetted auto shipping experts, ensuring your
                Motorcycle is transported by trusted members of the industry.
                These shipping companies will treat your motorcycle like their
                own.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <img src="/img/dollar.webp" class="w-24 h-20 mb-2" />
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold">Zero upfront payment</h5>
              <p class="xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0">
                You read that right, $0! We only charge your motorcycle
                transport cost once the carrier has been dispatched to your
                location.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
            <img src="/img/call.webp" class="w-24 h-24 mb-2" />
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold">Dedicated advisors</h5>
              <p class="xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0">
                Our team of professional shipping advisors are committed to
                locating the best carrier solution for every motorcycle we
                transport. We will monitor your shipment around the clock.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="w-[95%] xs:w-full sm:w-full wow"
          data-aos="fade-right"
          data-aos-delay="100"
          style="min-height: 400px;"
        >
          <div class="h-full">
            <img
              src="/img/moto2.jpg"
              class="object-cover rounded-xl w-full h-[60%]"
              alt=""
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <SecondFooter />
  <ButtonScrollTop client:load />
</Layout>
</body>
